[[鄧炳強|鄧炳強]]在2020年1月16日[[中西區區議會|中西區區議會]]會議中表示警方正循[[假口供|假口供]]的方向調查<ref>{{Cite web|title=少女報稱荃灣警署內遭強姦 鄧炳強：循誤導或假口供方向調查|url=https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/422752/少女報稱荃灣警署內遭強姦-鄧炳強-循誤導或假口供方向調查|accessdate=2020-01-19|date=2020-01-16|last=麥凱茵|work=香港01|language=zh-HK|archive-date=2020-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329012409/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/422752/%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%A0%B1%E7%A8%B1%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%85%A7%E9%81%AD%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7-%E5%BE%AA%E8%AA%A4%E5%B0%8E%E6%88%96%E5%81%87%E5%8F%A3%E4%BE%9B%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5|dead-url=no}}</ref>。受害少女在2日後透過韋智達律師行發出聲明，指對[[鄧炳強|鄧炳強]]的說法十分難過<ref name="荃灣警署輪姦_星島">{{Cite web|title=少女稱荃灣警署內被強姦 斥鄧炳強圖公開抹黑|url=http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1183492/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E7%A8%B1%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%85%A7%E8%A2%AB%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E6%96%A5%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E5%9C%96%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91|accessdate=2020-01-19|last=星島日報|work=std.stheadline.com|language=en}}</ref><ref name="荃灣警署輪姦_明報">{{Cite web|title=荃灣警署輪姦案鄧炳強稱查假口供 事主譴責損聲譽礙成功檢控 (20:50) - 20200118 - 港聞|url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200118/s00001/1579341853116/%e8%8d%83%e7%81%a3%e8%ad%a6%e7%bd%b2%e8%bc%aa%e5%a7%a6%e6%a1%88%e9%84%a7%e7%82%b3%e5%bc%b7%e7%a8%b1%e6%9f%a5%e5%81%87%e5%8f%a3%e4%be%9b-%e4%ba%8b%e4%b8%bb%e8%ad%b4%e8%b2%ac%e6%90%8d%e8%81%b2%e8%ad%bd%e7%a4%99%e6%88%90%e5%8a%9f%e6%aa%a2%e6%8e%a7|accessdate=2020-01-19|work=明報新聞網 - 即時新聞 instant news|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2020-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200119131709/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200118/s00001/1579341853116/%e8%8d%83%e7%81%a3%e8%ad%a6%e7%bd%b2%e8%bc%aa%e5%a7%a6%e6%a1%88%e9%84%a7%e7%82%b3%e5%bc%b7%e7%a8%b1%e6%9f%a5%e5%81%87%e5%8f%a3%e4%be%9b-%e4%ba%8b%e4%b8%bb%e8%ad%b4%e8%b2%ac%e6%90%8d%e8%81%b2%e8%ad%bd%e7%a4%99%e6%88%90%e5%8a%9f%e6%aa%a2%e6%8e%a7|dead-url=no}}</ref>。又譴責[[鄧炳強|鄧炳強]]試圖公開[[抹黑|抹黑]]她以貶損她的投訴並影響起訴成功的機會<ref name="荃灣警署輪姦_星島"/><ref name="荃灣警署輪姦_明報"/>，更漠視投訴人的私隱以及[[性暴力|性暴力]]受害者的尊嚴<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|title=報稱荃灣警署被警輪姦成孕少女 X 透過律師發聲明 譴責鄧炳強公開抹黑 {{!}} 立場報道 {{!}} 立場新聞|url=https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A0%B1%E7%A8%B1%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E8%BC%AA%E5%A7%A6%E6%88%90%E5%AD%95%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3-x-%E9%80%8F%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91/|accessdate=2020-01-19|work=立場新聞 Stand News|language=en|archive-date=2020-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200119155532/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A0%B1%E7%A8%B1%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E8%A2%AB%E8%AD%A6%E8%BC%AA%E5%A7%A6%E6%88%90%E5%AD%95%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3-x-%E9%80%8F%E9%81%8E%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E6%8A%B9%E9%BB%91/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===警方被指違反《罪行受害者約章》拒絕提供案件進度===

受害少女表示，她已經做了法醫檢驗，從墮胎胚胎提取施害者的DNA樣本。但警方一直無通知她有否從政府化驗所取得被指控施暴的警員們的DNA報告。她回答了警方一連串鉅細無遺及相當尖銳的問題，但警方在她不斷追問下仍然拒絕提供調查進度，也沒有表示他們是否有向律政司索取意見以及案件調查是否已經告一段落。她表示警方這些行為皆違反了《[https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/04_crime_matters/vic_charter.html 罪行受害者約章]{{Wayback|url=https://www.police.gov.hk/ppp_tc/04_crime_matters/vic_charter.html |date=20210315034611 }}》對受害者承諾的權利<ref name="#1"/>。

=== 邓炳强再度公開發言 ===
2020年5月12日，邓炳强在会议中表示，律政司指示他们，需就该少女「提供虚假口供」进行拘捕，但称其已经潜逃他地，现正通缉<ref>{{Cite web|title=少女稱荃灣警署內被強姦 鄧炳強：涉假口供正通緝|url=https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1769266/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E7%A8%B1%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%85%A7%E8%A2%AB%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7-%E6%B6%89%E5%81%87%E5%8F%A3%E4%BE%9B%E6%AD%A3%E9%80%9A%E7%B7%9D|accessdate=2020-05-12|author=|date=2020-05-12|format=|publisher=头条新闻|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2021-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315034617/https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1769266/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E7%A8%B1%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%85%A7%E8%A2%AB%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E9%84%A7%E7%82%B3%E5%BC%B7-%E6%B6%89%E5%81%87%E5%8F%A3%E4%BE%9B%E6%AD%A3%E9%80%9A%E7%B7%9D|dead-url=no}}</ref>。受害少女回應「她應該獲得警方對她如一名性暴力受害者，而非被這名中年男性的警務處處長如此可恥地對待」<ref name="憂人身安全離港">{{cite news |title=報案荃灣警署內被強姦　文匯報指已赴台灣　消息人士：X 小姐憂人身安全離港，從不知被通緝 |url=https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%A0%B1%E6%A1%88%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%85%A7%E8%A2%AB%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E6%96%87%E5%8C%AF%E5%A0%B1%E6%8C%87%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E5%B7%B2%E5%BE%80%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB-x-%E5%B0%8F%E5%A7%90%E6%86%82%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%9B%A2%E6%B8%AF-%E5%BE%9E%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%9A%E7%B7%9D/ |publisher=立場新聞 |date=2020-05-14 |accessdate=2020-05-14 |archive-date=2020-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200519230244/https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%A0%B1%E6%A1%88%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%85%A7%E8%A2%AB%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E6%96%87%E5%8C%AF%E5%A0%B1%E6%8C%87%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E5%B7%B2%E5%BE%80%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB-x-%E5%B0%8F%E5%A7%90%E6%86%82%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%9B%A2%E6%B8%AF-%E5%BE%9E%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%9A%E7%B7%9D/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，消息亦指受害少女憂人身安全離港，亦從不知自己被通緝<ref name="憂人身安全離港"/>。有評論質疑若事件真